column2: select t.albumid, count (*) as num, count (distinct composer) as numC from chinook.track t group by t.albumid) select * from r join chinook.track t on t.albumid = r.albumid join chinook.album b on b.albumid = t.albumid join chinook.artist a on a.artistid = b.artistid where r.numC between # and # order by r.num
